addr="jms-00KF"
title="Function">Functions</fr:link> are closed under <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00II.xml"
addr="jms-00II"
title="The identity relation">identity</fr:link> and <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00IN.xml"
